        Default constructor. Note that this does not initialize fields to their default values from the schema. If that is desired then one should use newBuilder().

      • SensorData

        public SensorData​(CharSequence sensorId,
                  CharSequence equipmentId,
                  Long timestamp,
                  Double temperature,
                  Double pressure,
                  CharSequence unit,
                  CharSequence location,
                  SensorStatus status,
                  Map<CharSequence,​CharSequence> metadata)
        All-args constructor.
        Parameters:
        sensorId - Unique identifier for the sensor device
        equipmentId - Identifier for the equipment this sensor is attached to
        timestamp - Unix timestamp in seconds when reading was taken
        temperature - Temperature reading value
        pressure - Optional pressure reading value
        unit - Measurement unit (e.g., Celsius, Fahrenheit, PSI)
        location - Physical location of the sensor
        status - Operational status of the sensor
        metadata - Additional sensor metadata
